divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my car coming back from the mall and my eye got caught by a bright light. My eyes focused on it. It was a Saturn-like object with a bright yellow light in the middle of the rings. There were two blinking lights around it. The object stayed up for about one minute and then zoomed away. While the object was in the air, everything was silent.
